{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "000f300a-47af-4b70-a16a-1196d450078c", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/000f300a-47af-4b70-a16a-1196d450078c@4.pkg/1772602094577/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602095112", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/000f300a-47af-4b70-a16a-1196d450078c@4.pkg/1772602094577/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602095112"}, "identifier": "000f300a-47af-4b70-a16a-1196d450078c", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>1.&nbsp;选项A：<br />\n- 句中“也要流进四方街”表达的是“我”的心愿，它前面缺少冒号来提示下文是心愿内容。一般像这种提示某人的想法、心愿等情况，要用冒号，所以A项标点使用错误。<br />\n2.&nbsp;选项B：<br />\n- “丽江坝”是对“山下绿色的盆地”的补充说明，这里应该用破折号而不是逗号；“森林”“田野”“村庄”是并列关系，中间应该用顿号而不是逗号 ，所以B项标点使用错误。<br />\n3.&nbsp;选项C：<br />\n- 句中所有标点使用正确，句子表达清晰，没有标点运用不当的问题。<br />\n4.&nbsp;选项D：<br />\n- “他们内心也很喧哗”后面的逗号使用不当，这里句子表达的是两个不同的意思层次，前面说在远方时内心喧哗，后面说在这里的情况，“他们内心也很喧哗”后应该用分号来区分层次，所以D项标点使用错误。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n答案：C。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>下列标点使用正确的一项是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "下列标点使用正确的一项是（    ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/000f300a-47af-4b70-a16a-1196d450078c@4.pkg/item.json?v=1753066410162", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>我记起了跌进落水洞前的心愿，也要流进四方街。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>我望见了山下绿色的盆地，丽江坝，望见了森林，田野和村庄。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>是的，我又化成了一滴水，和瀑布里另外的水大声喧哗着扑向山下。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>即便是寂静时分，他们内心也很喧哗，在这里，尽情欢歌处，夜凉如水，他们的心像一滴水一样晶莹。</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>下列标点使用正确的一项是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "$RE0200", "5036342748", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "000f300a-47af-4b70-a16a-1196d450078c", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列标点使用正确的一项是（    ）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>下列标点使用正确的一项是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status":